title: MasterChef.The.Professionals.S07E06.PDTVx264.mp4
description: Six chefs battle it out in the second quarter-final and the judges ask them to make dishes of their own invention from kitchen scraps, including bones and offcuts, fish skins, overripe fruit, cooked rice, cheese and stale bread. After an elimination, the remaining contestants have to cook two courses for food critics Tracey MacLeod, Jay Rayner and William Sitwell, before finding out who is going through to the semi-finals
